FBIS3-38422 "drweu022_h_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 GERMANY Kohl Warns Croatia Not To Use Regular Troops in Bosnia AU0102210294 Mainz ZDF Television Network in German 1800 GMT 1 Feb 94 AU0102210294 Mainz ZDF Television Network Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Chancellor Helmut Kohl has warned the Croatian leadership against using regular troops in the civil war in Bosnia. If corresponding reports should be confirmed, practical ways will be found to express Western disapproval, Kohl stated in Washington.
